---
title: Quick Chicken & Creamy Leek Sauce with Mashed Potato
description: Serve up a comforting meal that's as good as a hug! With tender, flavoursome leek in a creamy sauce and loads of satisfying
mash, this dinner will make you feel all snuggly - perfect for a home-cooked meal with heart.
